@page "/hamming-code-calculator"

@using Kryptos.Web.Client.Components.HammingCode
@using Kryptos.Web.Client.Components.HammingCode.EncodeForm
@using Kryptos.Web.Client.Components.HammingCode.DecodeForm

<PageTitle>Kryptos | Hamming Code</PageTitle>

<section>
    <h2 class="block mb-2 text-5xl font-medium tracking-widest uppercase lg:text-center dark:text-violet-400">
        Hamming Code Calculator
    </h2>
    <span class="block text-xl font-bold lg:text-center dark:text-gray-50">
        Error detection & correction
    </span>
</section>
<section class="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2">
    <div class="p-8 space-y-8 rounded-md lg:col-span-full lg:py-12">
        <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold dark:text-gray-50">Introduction</h2>
        <p class="dark:text-gray-400">
            Hamming code is a block code that is capable of detecting up to two simultaneous bit errors and correctiong
            single-bit errors. It was developed by R.W. Hamming for error detection and correction.
        </p>
        <p class="dark:text-gray-400">
            In this coding method, the source encodes the message by inserting redundant bits within the message.
            These redundant bits are extra bits that are generated and inserted at specific positions in the message
            itself to enable error detection and correction. When the destination recieves this message, it performs
            calculations to detect errors and find the position that has an error.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2">
    <div class="p-8 space-y-8 rounded-md lg:col-span-full lg:py-12 dark:bg-gray-900">
        <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold dark:text-gray-10">Explanation</h2>
        <TabControl>
            <TabPage Text="Encode">
                <EncodeSteps/>
            </TabPage>

            <TabPage Text="Decode">
                <DecodeSteps/>
            </TabPage>
        </TabControl>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2">
    <div class="p-8 space-y-8 rounded-md lg:col-span-full lg:py-12">
        <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold dark:text-gray-50">Example</h2>
        <TabControl>
            <TabPage Text="Encode">
                <EncodeForm />
            </TabPage>

            <TabPage Text="Decode">
                <DecodeForm />
            </TabPage>
        </TabControl>
    </div>
</section>